Package: ubuntu-express-ubuntu-doc
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Provides: ubuntu-express-doc
Description: Ubuntu Documentation and help files for Ubuntu Express Live installer
 This package provides a set of help files, html pages for the Ubuntu Express
 UI, text messages for the installer and more stuff related to Ubuntu
 distribution.

